    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You are not ready !</strong></h2><br>Try the <strong>H.A.R.D.</strong> experience : the Horrible Adventure Really Difficult. In this &quot;die &amp; retry&quot;, you'll surpass yourself, playing a hard but fun game with different functionalities.<br><br>Learn how to get the most from the simple controls to cross the <strong>40 levels</strong> : avoid red places and saws and reach the flag to complete a level. To succeed, you can move left and right and <strong>change the direction of the gravity</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Different functionalities :</strong></h2><br>When you become familiar with the controls, H.A.R.D. becomes insanely more difficult by adding features, which can be combined :<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137640/extras/64bb2ab0124d67c13c4c970c2e6ef1f1.avif?t=1745470388\" width=600 height=68 /></span><br><br>When you see a turned on pictogram, be careful ! Your <strong>controls may be reversed</strong> or the ground may be slippery.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Have fun playing H.A.R.D. ! And good luck...</strong></h2>",
